}</style><article id="post-18127" class="post-18127 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-all-recipes category-american category-chicken category-dinner category-gluten-free category-main-course category-nut-free category-one-bowl-recipes category-skillet category-sugar-free infinite-scroll-item no-featured-image-padding" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" itemscope><div class="inside-article"><header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</h1></header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-snippet wprm-recipe-template-snippet-basic-buttons"><a href="#recipe" data-recipe="18123" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-jump wprm-recipe-link wprm-jump-to-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-jump-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-jump-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g class="nc-icon-wrapper" fill="#ffffff"><path data-color="color-2" d="M9,2h6c0.6,0,1-0.4,1-1s-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,0,8,0.4,8,1S8.4,2,9,2z"></path> <path fill="#ffffff" d="M16,11V5c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1H9C8.4,4,8,4.4,8,5v6H1.9L12,23.6L22.1,11H16z"></path></g></svg></span> Jump to Recipe</a><a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wprm_print/paprika-chicken-comfort-bowl" style="color: #ffffff;background-color: #000000;border-color: #333333;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px 8px;" class="wprm-recipe-print wprm-recipe-link wprm-print-recipe-shortcode wprm-block-text-normal wprm-recipe-print-inline-button wprm-recipe-link-inline-button wprm-color-accent" data-recipe-id="18123" data-template="" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="wprm-recipe-icon wprm-recipe-print-icon"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" x="0px" y="0px" width="16px" height="16px" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><g ><path fill="#ffffff" d="M19,5.09V1c0-0.552-0.448-1-1-1H6C5.448,0,5,0.448,5,1v4.09C2.167,5.569,0,8.033,0,11v7c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h4v4c0,0.552,0.448,1,1,1h12c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-4h4c0.552,0,1-0.448,1-1v-7C24,8.033,21.833,5.569,19,5.09z M7,2h10v3H7V2z M17,22H7v-9h10V22z M18,10c-0.552,0-1-0.448-1-1c0-0.552,0.448-1,1-1s1,0.448,1,1C19,9.552,18.552,10,18,10z"/></g></svg></span> Print Recipe</a></div><p>This <strong>Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</strong> brings classic comfort to your table with modern ease, delivering a soul-warming meal that feels like a hug in a bowl. It&#x2019;s a one-pan wonder that simplifies your dinner routine while preserving all the traditional flavors you love.</p><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-122" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="under_page_title"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(122); });</script><img decoding="async" class="gb-media-40ed59d0" src="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Easy-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl.webp" alt="Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl recipe finished dish" title="Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl recipe" /><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="why-love-box"><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="your-new-favorite-comfort-bowl">Your New Favorite Comfort Bowl</h2><ul><li><strong>One-Pan Simplicity</strong> &#x2013; Everything cooks together for easy prep and even easier cleanup.</li><li><strong>Deep, Smoky Flavor</strong> &#x2013; The paprika creates a rich, cozy sauce that&#x2019;s incredibly satisfying.</li><li><strong>Weeknight Ready</strong> &#x2013; This easy chicken dinner comes together in about 50 minutes.</li><li><strong>Wholesome &#038; Filling</strong> &#x2013; Packed with lean protein and fluffy rice for a truly balanced meal.</li></ul></div><div class="wp-block-rank-math-toc-block" id="rank-math-toc"><h2>Table of Contents</h2><nav><ul><li><a href="#ready-for-cozy-comfort-in-under-an-hour">Ready for Cozy Comfort in Under an Hour</a></li><li><a href="#thoughtful-tips-for-special-diets">Thoughtful Tips for Special Diets</a></li><li><a href="#my-pro-tips-for-a-perfect-paprika-chicken-comfort-bowl">My Pro Tips for a Perfect Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</a></li><li><a href="#nourishing-your-body-with-comfort">Nourishing Your Body with Comfort</a></li><li><a href="#a-lighter-version-for-everyday-enjoyment">A Lighter Version for Everyday Enjoyment</a></li><li><a href="#serving-your-paprika-chicken-comfort-bowl-with-cozy-flair">Serving Your Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl with Cozy Flair</a></li><li><a href="#common-mistakes-and-how-to-avoid-them">Common Mistakes (And How to Avoid Them)</a></li><li><a href="#keeping-the-comfort-going-storage-tips">Keeping the Comfort Going: Storage Tips</a></li><li><a href="#more-cozy-chicken-dinners-youll-adore">More Cozy Chicken Dinners You&#8217;ll Adore</a></li><li><a href="#frequently-asked-questions">Frequently Asked Questions</a></li></ul></nav></div><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-youll-need-for-your-paprika-chicken-comfort-bowl">What You&#8217;ll Need for Your <strong>Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</strong></h2><section class="ingredient-group" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><h3 class="wp-block-heading">For the Chicken &#038; Spice Rub</h3><ul style="list-style: disc; margin:0 0 18px 20px; line-height:1.8;"><li><strong>Paprika</strong> &#8211; The star of the show, providing that signature smoky flavor and vibrant color.</li><li><strong>Garlic Powder</strong> &#8211; Adds a foundational savory note that complements the paprika perfectly.</li><li><strong>Onion Powder</strong> &#8211; Enhances the overall depth of flavor in the spice rub.</li><li><strong>Chicken Breasts</strong> &#8211; A lean protein base that stays tender and juicy in the creamy paprika skillet.</li></ul><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-130" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="under_first_paragraph"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(130); });</script></section><section class="ingredient-group" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><h3 class="wp-block-heading">For the Bowl Base &#038; Sauce</h3><ul style="list-style: disc; margin:0 0 18px 20px; line-height:1.8;"><li><strong>Long-Grain White Rice</strong> &#8211; Absorbs all the delicious flavors and creates a fluffy foundation.</li><li><strong>Chicken Broth</strong> &#8211; Cooks the rice while adding an extra layer of savory depth.</li><li><strong>Yellow Onion &#038; Red Bell Pepper</strong> &#8211; Sweet aromatics that soften into the dish beautifully.</li><li><strong>Sour Cream</strong> &#8211; Swirled in at the end for a luxuriously creamy sauce component.</li><li><strong>Fresh Parsley</strong> &#8211; A bright, fresh garnish that adds a pop of color and flavor.</li></ul></section><img decoding="async" class="gb-media-903e84a1" src="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Delicious-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl.webp" alt="Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl ingredients preparation" title="Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl ingredients" /><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ready-for-cozy-comfort-in-under-an-hour">Ready for Cozy Comfort in Under an Hour</h2><p>I love how this <strong>Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</strong> fits perfectly into a busy weeknight. With just 15 minutes of prep and 35 minutes of mostly hands-off cooking, you can have a feel-good classic on the table in about 50 minutes total. This timing is ideal for a stress-free family dinner.</p><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-131" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="under_second_paragraph"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(131); });</script><p>The active time is minimal, giving you a moment to relax while the rice simmers and the chicken finishes cooking. Compared to more complex comfort food recipes, this one-pan chicken rice method is a true soul-preserving shortcut. For another quick and flavorful option, try my <a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/honey-garlic-chicken-thighs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">honey garlic chicken thighs</a> on those especially hectic evenings.</p><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="thoughtful-tips-for-special-diets">Thoughtful Tips for Special Diets</h2><p>Creating meals that everyone can enjoy is so important to me. This recipe is naturally quite friendly for those watching their sugar intake, as it contains no added sugars. The carbohydrates primarily come from the rice, which provides sustained energy.</p><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-132" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="mid_content"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(132); });</script><p>For an even lower glycemic impact, you could swap the white rice for cauliflower rice added in the last few minutes of cooking. Using a sugar-free chicken broth ensures the dish remains truly sugar-conscious. Portion control is also a simple way to manage carbohydrate intake while still enjoying this cozy meal.</p><div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height:15px" aria-hidden="true"></div><h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="my-pro-tips-for-a-perfect-paprika-chicken-comfort-bowl">My Pro Tips for a Perfect <strong>Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</strong></h2><p>After making this comforting dish countless times, I&#x2019;ve gathered a few secrets to make it truly foolproof. These small tweaks can elevate your comfort bowl dinner from good to unforgettable.</p><ul><li><strong>Boost the Flavor:</strong> For a deeper taste, use smoked paprika instead of sweet. It adds a wonderful warmth that makes this healthy paprika chicken even more satisfying.</li><li><strong>Make it Creamier:</strong> If you love a richer sauce, stir in an extra tablespoon or two of sour cream at the end. This is the secret to a truly luxurious creamy paprika skillet.</li><li><strong>Avoid Mushy Rice:</strong> Be sure to use long-grain rice, as it holds its texture better than short-grain varieties. Let the dish rest for 5 minutes after cooking for the perfect fluffiness, a technique I also use in my <a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/smothered-chicken-and-rice/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">smothered chicken and rice</a>.</li><li><strong>Reheat Like a Pro:</strong> Store leftovers in an airtight container. Reheat gently on the stove with a splash of broth to keep the rice from drying out, similar to the method for this <a href="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/chicken-alfredo-rice-casserole/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">chicken alfredo rice casserole</a>.</li></ul><div id="ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-133" data-inserter-version="2" data-placement-location="long_content"></div><script data-ezoic="1" data-no-optimize="1" data-no-defer="1">ezstandalone.cmd.push(function () { ezstandalone.showAds(133); });</script><p><div id="recipe"></div><div id="wprm-recipe-container-18123" class="wprm-recipe-container" data-recipe-id="18123" data-servings="4"><div class="wprm-recipe wprm-recipe-template-ewpgls"><div class="wprm-recipe-image wprm-block-image-rounded"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: #666666;border-radius: 0px;width: 1000px;max-width: 100%;height: 400px;object-fit: cover;" width="896" height="1344" src="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Easy-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl.webp" class="attachment-1000x999999 size-1000x999999" alt="Easy Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl" srcset="https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Easy-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl.webp 896w, https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Easy-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl-200x300.webp 200w, https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Easy-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl-683x1024.webp 683w, https://www.allsavoryrecipes.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Easy-Paprika-Chicken-Comfort-Bowl-768x1152.webp 768w" sizes="(max-width: 896px) 100vw, 896px" /></div><div class="wprm-layout-container wprm-padding-40"><div class="wprm-layout-column-container wprm-align-middle wprm-column-gap-10 wprm-column-rows-recipe-500"><div class="wprm-layout-column wprm-align-rows-center"><h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Paprika Chicken Comfort Bowl</h2></div><div class="wprm-layout-column wprm-align-right wprm-align-rows-center" style="--wprm-layout-column-text-color: var(--glacier-accent-color);">
